"Eligible Applicants|Australia Undergraduate Scholarship\">Eligible Applicants|Australia Undergraduate Scholarship<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/australia-undergraduate-scholarship\/#How_to_apply_for_the_online_Australia_Undergraduate_Scholarship\" title=\"How to apply for the online Australia Undergraduate Scholarship\">How to apply for the online Australia Undergraduate Scholarship<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><strong>The Australia Scholarships Admission for Undergraduate is ongoing for an interested applicant; learn more about Australia scholarships admission requirements, a program of studies, application fees:<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80172884\">How to get a scholarship in Australia<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80172885\">Percentage Required for Scholarship in Australia<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80172886\">Required CGPA<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80172887\">What GPA is required for a scholarship in Australia?<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80172888\">English language proficiency<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80172889\">Eligible Applicants<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80172890\">How to apply online<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-get-a-scholarship-in-australia\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_get_a_scholarship_in_Australia\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80172884\"><\/a>How to get a scholarship in Australia<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Participate in community life<\/li>\n<li>Apply for as many scholarships<\/li>\n<li>Ask for help with applications<\/li>\n<li>Read the scholarship criteria carefully<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"percentage-required-for-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Percentage_Required_for_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80172885\"><\/a>Percentage Required for Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Applicants should have a minimum of 85% in the previous degree\/high school.<\/li>\n<li>Meet the eligible English language requirements of the course applying and have an offer for admission by the university.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"required-cgpaaustralia-undergraduate-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Required_CGPAAustralia_Undergraduate_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80172886\"><\/a>Required CGPA|Australia Undergraduate Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>For scholarships, candidates who score 60% are eligible for a scholarship test, or the highest marks are considered if no test is involved.<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"what-gpa-is-required-for-a-scholarship-in-australia\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_GPA_is_required_for_a_scholarship_in_Australia\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80172887\"><\/a>What GPA is required for a scholarship in Australia?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>A GPA of at least 3.00 is required<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"english-language-proficiency\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"English_language_proficiency\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80172888\"><\/a>English language proficiency<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>IELTS: an aggregate score of 6.5 is accepted and 6.0 in general<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"eligible-applicantsaustralia-undergraduate-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Eligible_ApplicantsAustralia_Undergraduate_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80172889\"><\/a>Eligible Applicants|Australia Undergraduate Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>The applicants should be:<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>An Indian national with a valid Indian passport<\/li>\n<li>Below 35 years of age before 31 January in the year of application<\/li>\n<li>Holding a master\u2019s (postgraduate) degree from a recognized Indian institution with a first-class award (UG and PG) in the relevant subject\/field.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-apply-for-the-online-australia-undergraduate-scholarship\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_apply_for_the_online_Australia_Undergraduate_Scholarship\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80172890\"><\/a>How to apply for the online Australia Undergraduate Scholarship<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>National Scholarship portal registration<\/li>\n<li>Logging in with the National Scholarship portal<\/li>\n<li>Change the password (a compulsory step)<\/li>\n<li>Enter the dashboard &amp; complete the application<\/li>\n<li>New student registration<\/li>\n<li>Student login.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>For more information visit <a href=\"https:\/\/www.scholars4dev.com\/4950\/australia-scholarships\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a> to learn more about and to apply.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>See also&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.applyjobs.org.ng\/unb-graduate-programs-university-of-new-brunswick\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">UNB Graduate Programs \/University of New Brunswick<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Australia \u00a0Undergraduate Scholarship \u2013Online Application for Undergraduate, Australia Application login, Application fees, Deadlines, Program requirements, and academic qualifications&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1407,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[448],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1406"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-jso